caption.p:
Effect of RTL-EAF5 fractions on glucose uptake in mouse FL83B hepatocytes. Each value is mean ± SD ( n = 3). C (control): FL83B cells incubated with F-12K medium. T (TNF- α treatment): FL83B cells incubated with F-12K medium containing TNF- α (20 ng/ml) for 16 hours to induce insulin resistance. EAF5s: TNF- α induced insulin resistance and then coincubated with RTL-EAF5 fractions (25 µg/ml) for 30 min.
∗ Significantly different from control ( P < 0.05).
